Author: balehubucks
Body: Our Bounty Program has officially been launched and the response has been terrific.  With everything now in place, we are looking forward to the start of our Pre-ICO.

Author: Stephlambert
Body: Too bad you are launching a Bounty campaign just now when your preICO is less than 24 hours away. That's very little time to raise awareness around your project and reach potential investors. What is the softcap for the preICO?

Author: balehubucks
Body: The Pre-ICO does not have a soft cap.  We are expected to raise 3,000 ETH during the Pre-ICO, which will run until we hit 3,000 ETH or 8 weeks, whichever comes first.  Our journey is just beginning toward our ICO date of Feb. 1 2018, so you will have plenty of time to participate in our bounty program if you so choose.

Author: Stephlambert
Body: I see. That is a bit unlikely as most preICO/ICO have both a soft and hard cap. On what base do you expect to reach 3,000 ETH? Don't get me wrong, I wish the team success, but a preICO that is leveraging virtually no social media campaign or awareness somehow, I believe it will be tough to reach 3k ETH. You should have started the bounty a month before the preICO or so imho.

Author: balehubucks
Body: Thank you for your input.  We are focusing our marketing effort in very strategic places.  The bounty program has been a success so far and is only 1 piece of the overall picture.
